{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"95dbdf889a","title":"林彪关于旅大地区的三点指示","origin":"（据五月十三日海军新党委给海工红团电报）\n    摘自北大《北斗星》","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ecc9ca183c","index":0,"year":1968,"month":5,"day":8,"articleId":"95dbdf889a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"5f6c7e74b5","name":"派性","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f326d8be5e","name":"林彪"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"0847e486af","type":"title","text":"关于旅大地区的三点指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"7557449366","type":"authors","text":"林彪","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"1a95fbeab9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、军队无论如何不能开枪，防止坏人挑拨我们开枪犯错误，千万不要上当。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"263c5d7fb1","type":"paragraph","text":"二、要继续克服资产阶级派性，一定要—碗水端平，不要支—派、压一派。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"dbde114b36","type":"paragraph","text":"三、当前特别重要的是继续抓好工人队伍工作，有了军队，有了工人阶级，有就能稳定局势，我们什么都不怕。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"79df3234fc","type":"paragraph","text":"（据五月十三日海军新党委给海工红团电报）","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"},{"id":"7b05f69c55","type":"paragraph","text":"摘自北大《北斗星》","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a"}],"page":{"id":"4f07bc82ca","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"95dbdf889a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}